s=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportTopicButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2525978\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2525978\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Juli 21, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104bcx1665702569415.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/bcx1665702569415.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/bcx1665702569415.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"bcx1665702569415\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      urm copy\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Copy files from a source to a target directory or zip file.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"bcx1665702569415__topic_d176774e1_d176775e1_d176776e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"bcx1665702569415__p_d176777e1_d176778e1_d176779e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">urm</span> {<var class=\"keyword varname\">Switches</var>} <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">copy</span>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Source</var>{+ <var class=\"keyword varname\">Source</var>}{<var class=\"keyword varname\">Destination</var>} {<var class=\"keyword varname\">Options</var>}</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"bcx1665702569415__section_o54_ln1_dcc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d244876e79\">Switches and Parameters</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">See <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"fpl1665702658861.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fpl1665702658861.html\" title=\"Executable for the Uniface Resource Manager, a command line utility for creating and manipulating Uniface archive files and other resources, files and DBMS tables.\">urm</a>.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"bcx1665702569415__section_mwv_nn1_dcc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d244876e95\">Options</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"bcx1665702569415__table_d18632e1_d18633e1_d18634e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"bcx1665702569415__table_d18632e1_d18633e1_d18634e1__entry__1\">Option</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"bcx1665702569415__table_d18632e1_d18633e1_d18634e1__entry__2\">Description</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"bcx1665702569415__table_d18632e1_d18633e1_d18634e1__entry__1\"><span class=\"keyword cmdname\">-silent</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"bcx1665702569415__table_d18632e1_d18633e1_d18634e1__entry__2\">Perform operations silently, without displaying\n                        messages.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"bcx1665702569415__table_d18632e1_d18633e1_d18634e1__entry__1\"><span class=\"keyword cmdname\">-noSubDir</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"bcx1665702569415__table_d18632e1_d18633e1_d18634e1__entry__2\">Do not process subdirectories</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"bcx1665702569415__table_d18632e1_d18633e1_d18634e1__entry__1\"><span class=\"keyword cmdname\">-after=</span>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">yyyymmdd</var> {<var class=\"keyword varname\">hhnnss</var>} |\n                           <code class=\"ph codeph\">today</code>\n<p class=\"p\"><span class=\"keyword cmdname\">-before=</span>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">yyyymmdd</var> {<var class=\"keyword varname\">hhnnss</var>} |\n                              <code class=\"ph codeph\">today</code>\n</p></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"bcx1665702569415__table_d18632e1_d18633e1_d18634e1__entry__2\">Specify date of files.<p class=\"p\">The following\n                           separators are allowed: <code class=\"ph codeph\">-</code> (hyphen), <code class=\"ph codeph\">/</code>\n                           (slash), and <code class=\"ph codeph\">:</code> (colon).</p><div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"bcx1665702569415__note_w5654ab1b5b1b1b1b7b5b3b2_w5655ab1b5b1b1b1b7b5b3_w5656ab1b5b1b1b1b7b5_w5657ab1b5b1b1b1b7_w5658ab1b5b1b1b1_w5659ab1b5b1b1_w5660ab1b5b1_w5661ab1b5_w5662ab1\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span> The date format differs from the\n      date format in the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/aft</span> and <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/bef</span> switches.</div></td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"bcx1665702569415__table_d18632e1_d18633e1_d18634e1__entry__1\"><span class=\"keyword cmdname\">-InputCharset=</span>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">CharSet</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"bcx1665702569415__table_d18632e1_d18633e1_d18634e1__entry__2\">Specify the input characters set</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"bcx1665702569415__table_d18632e1_d18633e1_d18634e1__entry__1\"><span class=\"keyword cmdname\">-XmlCharset=</span>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">CharSet</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"bcx1665702569415__table_d18632e1_d18633e1_d18634e1__entry__2\">Specify the XML characters set</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"bcx1665702569415__table_d18632e1_d18633e1_d18634e1__entry__1\"><span class=\"keyword cmdname\">-OutputCharset=</span>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">CharSet</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"bcx1665702569415__table_d18632e1_d18633e1_d18634e1__entry__2\">Specify the output characters set</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"bcx1665702569415__section_rhk_c41_dcc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d244876e243\">Converting Character Sets</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">Use the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">copy</span> command to convert the character set of one file to\n            another.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"bcx1665702569415__p_d176792e1_d176793e1_d176794e1\">For example, the following command converts the\n            file <span class=\"ph filepath\">MyFile.txt</span> from the Western European character set to the\n            Eastern European character set:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"bcx1665702569415__pre_p3v_241_dcc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">urm copy MyFile.txt -inputCharset=cp1252 -outputCharset=cp1250</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"bcx1665702569415__section_stn_1pm_gxb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d244876e264\">Example: Copying Objects </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"bcx1665702569415__p_d176798e1_d176799e1_d176800e1\">The following command copies a ReadMe file to\n               <span class=\"ph filepath\">MyArchive.uar</span>:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"bcx1665702569415__pre_v1h_2pm_gxb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">urm copy readme.txt MyArchive.uar:/myarchive.rme</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"bcx1665702569415__p_d176801e1_d176802e1_d176803e1\">The following command copies all subdirectories and\n            objects in the <span class=\"ph filepath\">MyObjects</span> directory to the\n               <span class=\"ph filepath\">MyArchive.uar</span> file.</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"bcx1665702569415__pre_hzf_fpm_gxb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">urm copy MyObjects/*/* MyArchive.uar:/*/*</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"bcx1665702569415__p_d176804e1_d176805e1_d176806e1\">The following command copies all objects in the\n               <span class=\"ph filepath\">MyArchive.uar</span> to the <span class=\"ph filepath\">MyObjects</span>\n            directory.</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"bcx1665702569415__pre_cwg_gpm_gxb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">urm copy MyArchive.uar:/*/* MyObjects/*/* </code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"bcx1665702569415__p_d176807e1_d176808e1_d176809e1\">The following command is useful for selecting only\n            updates since 28 August 2013:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"bcx1665702569415__pre_dwg_gpm_gxb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">urm copy *.* update/*.* -after=20130828</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2525978\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2525978\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "urm copy Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Juli 21, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 urm copy Copy files from a source to a target directory or zip file. urm { Switches } copy Source {+ Source }{ Destination } { Options } Switches and Parameters See urm . Options Option Description -silent Perform operations silently, without displaying messages. -noSubDir Do not process subdirectories -after= yyyymmdd { hhnnss } | today -before= yyyymmdd { hhnnss } | today Specify date of files. The following separators are allowed: - (hyphen), / (slash), and : (colon). Note: The date format differs from the date format in the /aft and /bef switches. -InputCharset= CharSet Specify the input characters set -XmlCharset= CharSet Specify the XML characters set -OutputCharset= CharSet Specify the output characters set Converting Character Sets Use the copy command to convert the character set of one file to another. For example, the following command converts the file MyFile.txt from the Western European character set to the Eastern European character set: urm copy MyFile.txt -inputCharset=cp1252 -outputCharset=cp1250 Copy Example: Copying Objects The following command copies a ReadMe file to MyArchive.uar : urm copy readme.txt MyArchive.uar:/myarchive.rme Copy The following command copies all subdirectories and objects in the MyObjects directory to the MyArchive.uar file. urm copy MyObjects/*/* MyArchive.uar:/*/* Copy The following command copies all objects in the MyArchive.uar to the MyObjects directory. urm copy MyArchive.uar:/*/* MyObjects/*/* Copy The following command is useful for selecting only updates since 28 August 2013: urm copy *.* update/*.* -after=20130828 Copy Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}